      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs=""/>Herrn D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Arthur Schnitzler</addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb68" type="place">Wien XVIII</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb168940" type="place">Spöttelgasse 7</rs></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="MS-B-00005-B-000-00190"/><date>7. 1. 04</date></dateline><salute>Lieber Arthur!</salute></opener><p>Kann<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Du mir die Adre<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e des D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs ref="#pmb2199" type="person">Stefan Ep<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tein</rs> in <rs ref="#pmb182" type="place">Paris</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chreiben? Bitte<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ei<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o lieb.</p><p>Mir gehts recht<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chlecht.</p><closer>Deine <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2173" subtype="implied">Frau</rs> be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tens
               grüßend bin ich<lb/>herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t<lb/>Dein alter<lb/><signed>HermannBahr</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
